{"tid":1454312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋人］你係示威者 就應該要比人搞架啦","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:23:16.000Z","uid":6788,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"45216088c0004d0628dc223eb621973096c30204","tid":1454312,"uid":6788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GRsxU7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GRsxU7.png&h=bf748bca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/144904_7f42fdd03e6cb43d62287dfa1231636e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F144904_7f42fdd03e6cb43d62287dfa1231636e.png&h=c7c57edd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/145012_7d1965a7466fe29eb9adf19c7d36c7f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F145012_7d1965a7466fe29eb9adf19c7d36c7f4.png&h=15616d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人識上面位橙衫英雄<br />\n<br />\n有能比佢諗到用非禮去撐驚撐政府<br />\n<br />\n有能比佢搞到MTR d cctv都失哂靈<br />\n<br />\n又有能比佢性騷擾完啲黑衫市民都可以全身而退<br />\n<br />\n驚狗都識英雄重英雄<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想親身搵佢拎個簽名以示G持<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以介紹佢比我識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af01e037f32940bfd72b6d8cdd466b2343e7cb6","tid":1454312,"uid":6788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"我都想佢教我點樣發洩"},{"pid":"1b01c1a313874b519daf8399b29aec38627233fc","tid":1454312,"uid":6788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"琴晚谷到成肚火 好需要撐驚撐政府咁發洩"},{"pid":"ec5049a758c71e0edb65313e2caf738bc177c811","tid":1454312,"uid":6788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"又高大又威猛"},{"pid":"bafa5a1f4888aa80da